DataElement.preferredDefinition: The right to obtain or make use of or take advantage of something (as services or membership); the right to enter.  Also, an act or means of A character string that provides the key details of the intervention. EXAMPLE(S): Interventions involving drugs may include dosage form, dosage, frequency and duration. (50 mg/m2, IV (in the vein) on day 5 of each 28 day cycle. Number of Cycles: until progression or unacceptable toxicity develops.).
